(213, 1, '2022-08-06 16:38:27', '2022-08-06 13:38:27', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>At first glance, especially to a person who does not understand the automotive world, this device will seem relatively simple in forms. Undoubtedly, it is more beautiful and aggressive than many cars of the same class, but still it is not McLaren or Ferrari with their smooth exotic silhouettes. Four doors, a spacious interior, a large trunk — it would seem, what is not the most ordinary car? But it is only necessary to press the starter button, as something happens, for which everyone fell in love with this car. Handling, speed, dynamics, loud, but at the same time very pleasant and clean engine sounds are not a complete list of what the driver of this car gets in addition to all practicality. Also, do not forget that BMW, as a premium brand, has placed some features in its car that further instill love for it.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'BMW M5 COMPETITION', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'bmw-m5-competition', '', '', '2022-08-06 16:38:28', '2022-08-06 13:38:28', '', 0, 'http://wordpress-carbook-training.ru/?post_type=car&#038;p=213', 0, 'car', '', 0),
