(225, 1, '2022-08-06 16:55:00', '2022-08-06 13:55:00', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The BMW M8 Gran Coupe is an amazing four—door sports car that combines the advanced engineering solutions of the BMW M family models and the exclusivity of BMW luxury cars, offers unprecedented driving pleasure and an indescribable atmosphere of luxury.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The most extravagant representative of the line — BMW M8 Competition Gran Coupe with the M xDrive system — is distinguished by exciting performance and luxury in the highest embodiment.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The 8-cylinder TwinPower Turbo petrol engine with a displacement of 4.4 liters, producing 625 hp, is the most powerful in the line of engines of BMW production cars. The characteristics of the BMW M8 Competition Gran Coupe power unit, equipped with two TwinScroll turbochargers, high-pressure injection systems and Valvetronic valve timing changes, are impressive both on public roads and on the race track: torque of 750 Nm, acceleration to 100 km/h in 3.2 seconds, and up to 200 km/hh in 11.0 seconds.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The progressive design of the BMW M8 Competition Gran Coupe is distinguished by radical and dynamic, but at the same time exceptionally elegant contours. The luxury and pronounced character of this four-door sports car cannot be overlooked. The best materials and the highest craftsmanship made it possible to make the interior really sporty and at the same time exclusively luxurious..</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'BMW M8 GRAN COUPE', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'bmw-m8-competition-gran-coupe', '', '', '2022-08-16 23:46:14', '2022-08-16 20:46:14', '', 0, 'http://wordpress-carbook-training.ru/?post_type=car&#038;p=225', 0, 'car', '', 0),
