(227, 1, '2022-08-06 17:01:01', '2022-08-06 14:01:01', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Do you dream of being behind the wheel of a premium crossover, which is considered one of the most expensive in its class? Then the Bentley Bentayga rental is created for you. This car is presented in a deep gray color, which emphasizes the combination of impressive dynamic body lines and a luxurious comfortable interior of combined colors.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The Bentley Bentayga in white is also presented in our fleet. They are distinguished not only by the color solutions of the exterior and interior, but also by the configuration. For more information, check with the managers when booking.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Among the main advantages of the Bentley Bentayga:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>revolutionary V-shaped 8-cylinder engine with twin-scroll turbochargers. It is distinguished by impressive power and responsiveness;<br>the All-Terrain package. This option combines advanced features and systems that expand the off-road capabilities of the car. It will give the driver maximum confidence in any situation;<br>excellent dynamics thanks to optional carbon-ceramic brakes. You will be able to feel completely safe.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'BENTLEY BENTAYGA', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'bentley-bentayga', '', '', '2022-08-17 00:11:26', '2022-08-16 21:11:26', '', 0, 'http://wordpress-carbook-training.ru/?post_type=car&#038;p=227', 0, 'car', '', 0),
