(438, 1, '2022-08-16 23:46:14', '2022-08-16 20:46:14', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The BMW M8 Gran Coupe is an amazing four—door sports car that combines the advanced engineering solutions of the BMW M family models and the exclusivity of BMW luxury cars, offers unprecedented driving pleasure and an indescribable atmosphere of luxury.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The most extravagant representative of the line — BMW M8 Competition Gran Coupe with the M xDrive system — is distinguished by exciting performance and luxury in the highest embodiment.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The 8-cylinder TwinPower Turbo petrol engine with a displacement of 4.4 liters, producing 625 hp, is the most powerful in the line of engines of BMW production cars. The characteristics of the BMW M8 Competition Gran Coupe power unit, equipped with two TwinScroll turbochargers, high-pressure injection systems and Valvetronic valve timing changes, are impressive both on public roads and on the race track: torque of 750 Nm, acceleration to 100 km/h in 3.2 seconds, and up to 200 km/hh in 11.0 seconds.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The progressive design of the BMW M8 Competition Gran Coupe is distinguished by radical and dynamic, but at the same time exceptionally elegant contours. The luxury and pronounced character of this four-door sports car cannot be overlooked. The best materials and the highest craftsmanship made it possible to make the interior really sporty and at the same time exclusively luxurious..</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'BMW M8 GRAN COUPE', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '225-revision-v1', '', '', '2022-08-16 23:46:14', '2022-08-16 20:46:14', '', 225, 'http://wordpress-carbook-training.ru/?p=438', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(439, 1, '2022-08-21 15:41:20', '2022-08-21 12:41:20', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>enting a Bentley Continental GTIII at the Octane Club is an opportunity to feel real freedom thanks to self–sufficient handling. The breathtaking speed and excellent performance of the air suspension give maximum pleasure from driving. By renting an updated version of this car in Moscow, you will be able to appreciate the most powerful characteristics of the power unit and the highest level of comfort.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you want to combine dynamic driving with an unsurpassed level of real English luxury, then you should definitely rent a Bentley Continental. This car combines everything you need to stand out in the stream:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>amazing look. The body, made of hot-molded aluminum, is distinguished by textured stamping and a shiny silhouette. Compartment without middle racks;<br>characteristic strokes. The number 12 is integrated behind the front wheels, characterizing the 12-cylinder model. When you open the doors, the Bentley logo is projected onto the ground;<br>safety. Motion control is provided by stunning optics and rear-view cameras. The night vision screen is located on the digital panel.<br>comfortable interior. Simply created for maximum comfort in management. But despite the coupe version, there is a place even for a group of friends who will undoubtedly want to share this trip with you. Materials deserve special attention: soft leather, comfortable seats, chrome-plated details and incredibly beautiful vents and watches.<br>Bentley Continental rental is a service available to Octane Club members and those who are just planning to join us. To get acquainted with our service, we have a special trial tariff for the first day. Take this car for a business meeting, for a wedding or for a walk around the city.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'BENTLEY CONTINENTAL GT III', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'bentley-continental-gt-iii', '', '', '2022-08-21 16:17:07', '2022-08-21 13:17:07', '', 0, 'http://wordpress-carbook-training.ru/?post_type=car&#038;p=439', 0, 'car', '', 0),
