(450, 1, '2022-08-21 16:29:51', '2022-08-21 13:29:51', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The Rolls-Royce Cullinan SUV is the second car of the brand on the innovative aluminum platform \"Architecture of Luxury\". The first such car was the Rolls-Royce Phantom. The possibilities of the \"Luxury Architecture\" are revealed in a new way in Cullinan, adding controllability, maneuverability and cross-country ability to the car.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The aluminum body frame is combined with an updated air suspension, which ensures smooth running, which has become the hallmark of the British brand. Rolls-Royce Cullinan is a unique and one-of-a-kind crossover in the \"ulta-lux\" class.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This is the second, newer model of our fleet, in black, equipped with a comfortable and interesting interior. In this model you will be able to appreciate: wood trim of the central part of the panel, front and rear seats with massage function, ceiling illumination \"Starry sky with flickering effect\", rear seats with separate adjustments, including a central console with a bar and refrigerator, tables with electric drive for rear passengers, Rolls-Royce Bespoke Audio system, package driver assistance, etc.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The car is presented in black with a double stripe on the body in Turchese color, the interior trim is made using the same color.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Rolls-Royce Cullinan is available for rent with or without a driver. Choose a convenient option and rental period for yourself and enjoy the comfort of a trip in the best Rolls-Royce traditions.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'ROLLS-ROYCE CULLINAN', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'rolls-royce-cullinan', '', '', '2022-08-21 16:33:10', '2022-08-21 13:33:10', '', 0, 'http://wordpress-carbook-training.ru/?post_type=car&#038;p=450', 0, 'car', '', 0),
