(453, 1, '2022-08-21 16:35:53', '2022-08-21 13:35:53', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Renting a Ghost in Moscow is an opportunity to feel the temper of a unique British car. This model does not need extra advertising, a detailed analysis of technical parameters or a banal enumeration of advantages. Every detail of this super-premium car speaks for itself. It is enough to rent a Rolls-Royce Gost to make sure of this personally.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The Oktan Club company offers Rolls-Royce Ghost rental with and without a driver. The first option is preferable for those who want to fully appreciate the luxurious interior of the car. Everything is fine in it: finishing with the finest leather, natural wood and alcantara, an advanced on-board computer with an LCD display and a lot of adjustments with an electric drive. Place an order, pay the rental price for a day or for a few hours, and then enjoy the character of the British brand. For the unrestrained temper in charge:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>uncompromising V12 engine with two turbocharged compressors;<br>the location of the power unit behind the front axle for optimal load distribution;<br>8-band automatic transmission ZF, which switches speeds taking into account the characteristics of the navigation system.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'ROLLS-ROYCE GHOST', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'rolls-royce-ghost', '', '', '2022-08-21 16:35:54', '2022-08-21 13:35:54', '', 0, 'http://wordpress-carbook-training.ru/?post_type=car&#038;p=453', 0, 'car', '', 0),
