(456, 1, '2022-08-21 16:40:13', '2022-08-21 13:40:13', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Wraith is the most powerful and fast model in the entire Rolls-Royce family. The brand has created a coupe in which timeless noble design is combined with unsurpassed dynamics, power and original aesthetics inspired by the bright personality of the founder of the company. The creators attributed the car to the \"grand turismo\" class, but there is no hint of brutality and rage of GT classics in it. He is maneuverable, strong, with a lively and dynamic temperament, but he remembers the comfort of the driver and passengers. This is a real gentleman who embodies a thirst for adventure, a love of risky speed and an impeccable appearance in which everything is thought out to the last detail.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Wraith has its own \"face\" and character — a little reminiscent of the aesthetics of noir, determined, internally ready for a decisive throw, like a champion before a competition. Its interior is reminiscent of premium oceanic yachts, and 1340 flickering diodes create the illusion of spending the night under the stars.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'ROLLS-ROYCE WRAITH', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'rolls-royce-wraith', '', '', '2022-08-21 16:40:13', '2022-08-21 13:40:13', '', 0, 'http://wordpress-carbook-training.ru/?post_type=car&#038;p=456', 0, 'car', '', 0),
