(463, 1, '2022-08-21 17:00:05', '2022-08-21 14:00:05', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Turbo GT rental is an opportunity to get into the spirit of motor sports. Get acquainted with the characteristics of this bright car to see for yourself. This is the fastest crossover that accelerates to 100 km/h in 3.3 seconds and is equipped with:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>adaptive air suspension with PASM;<br>updated titanium sports exhaust system and rear carbon diffuser;<br>active roll suppression system PDCC;<br>8-speed Tiptronic S transmission with electronic shift technology.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Renting this car will allow you not only to feel the sports drive, but also to feel maximum comfort. This was made possible thanks to the original Alcantara interior finish, which combines noble genuine leather and swift lines. Additional driving convenience is provided by comfortable racing seats with integrated headrests. Rent a new Porsche and enjoy its brusque character. No speed limits and driving style provided by the Octane Club.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'PORSCHE CAYENNE GT', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'porsche-cayenne-turbo-gt', '', '', '2022-08-21 17:04:26', '2022-08-21 14:04:26', '', 0, 'http://wordpress-carbook-training.ru/?post_type=car&#038;p=463', 0, 'car', '', 0),
