(466, 1, '2022-08-21 17:02:43', '2022-08-21 14:02:43', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The latest generation of the Porsche 911Turbo S received a new six- cylinder oppositionist of the previous volume of 3.8 liters. Two turbochargers with variable geometry of the working apparatus allow you to squeeze 650 hp and 800 Nm from the modular motor. This is 70 \"horses\" and 50 N • m more than the last 911 Turbo S of the 991 II series. Acceleration time to 100 km / h decreased by 0.2 seconds to 2.7, and acceleration to two hundred takes only 8.9 seconds, a second less than before. The maximum speed remained at 330 km/h. Rent a new Porsche 911. Test it, test yourself!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'PORSCHE 911 TURBO S', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'porsche-911-turbo-s', '', '', '2022-08-21 17:02:43', '2022-08-21 14:02:43', '', 0, 'http://wordpress-carbook-training.ru/?post_type=car&#038;p=466', 0, 'car', '', 0),
