(473, 1, '2022-08-21 19:03:14', '2022-08-21 16:03:14', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Porsche has developed the first fully electric car. It may become the most serious competitor for the Tesla Model S. The model is called the Porsche Taycan and is a fully electric sports sedan that promises to provide the owner with up to 750 horsepower, acceleration from zero to 100 km / h in 2.6 seconds and fast charging of an 800-volt battery – it will last for 450 km in accordance with the European test standard WLTP.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'PORSCHE TAYCAN TURBO S', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'porsche-taycan-turbo-s', '', '', '2022-08-21 19:03:15', '2022-08-21 16:03:15', '', 0, 'http://wordpress-carbook-training.ru/?post_type=car&#038;p=473', 0, 'car', '', 0),
