(479, 1, '2022-08-21 19:10:58', '2022-08-21 16:10:58', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Renting a Porsche Panamera GTS in a new body is a real pleasure from any maneuver. This is a luxurious dynamic car, in every line of which you can feel the power. A real revolution in the world of sports cars. The Porsche Panamera combines all the advantages that are necessary for comfort and dynamic driving:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>adaptive air suspension with PASM technology. It controls the stiffness and height of the shock absorbers in real time; </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>ceramic PCCB brakes. They guarantee traffic safety and fast braking of the car;<br>the Sport Chrono package. Just one click on the button is enough for the chassis, engine and gearbox to switch to sports mode;<br>soft spacious interior. There is enough space for the company of friends and family. At the same time there is a roomy trunk.<br>By renting this car, you will be able to enjoy its speed, dynamics and technological innovations.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'PORSCHE PANAMERA GTS', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'porsche-panamera-gts', '', '', '2022-08-21 19:10:58', '2022-08-21 16:10:58', '', 0, 'http://wordpress-carbook-training.ru/?post_type=car&#038;p=479', 0, 'car', '', 0),
