(488, 1, '2022-08-21 19:27:56', '2022-08-21 16:27:56', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Renting a Mercedes-Maybach GLS is an opportunity to get a legendary executive class SUV at your disposal. This car combines an exquisite interior, an elegant exterior and innovative technologies. Octane Club clients can rent a Maybach with or without a driver in Moscow. The rental period is from 8 hours to several days. An ideal option to rent a car for a wedding or honeymoon, VIP transfer, meeting guests at the airport or a business trip.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Renting a Mercedes Maybach in Moscow is a great option for any occasion. The delightful exterior, the nobility of which is emphasized by exquisite chrome details and branded attributes of the Maybahs, will tell everyone around about the high status of passengers. Mercedes Benz seats with massage functions and retractable illuminated footrests guarantee the highest level of comfort. An excellent sound insulation system will make the trip around the city quiet and peaceful. This is what everyone expects from the Mercedes-Benz Maybach GLS.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'MERCEDES-BENZ MAYBACH', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'mercedes-benz-gls-maybach', '', '', '2022-08-21 19:28:51', '2022-08-21 16:28:51', '', 0, 'http://wordpress-carbook-training.ru/?post_type=car&#038;p=488', 0, 'car', '', 0),
