(503, 1, '2022-08-21 22:06:30', '2022-08-21 19:06:30', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The AMG-specific radiator grille with its A-shaped outline enhances the impression of road-hugging breadth, just like the flat LED headlights. Wide-ranging restyling also makes the Saloon viewed from the rear look even more muscular. These include the two-part rear lights, the new rear apron and the new diffuser insert. The interior too takes on greater sportiness with its large displays, the new AMG performance steering wheel and the AMG-specific MBUX functions. The electrified 3.0-litre engine with twin turbocharging through an exhaust-driven turbo and an electric auxiliary compressor generates 320 kW (435 PS) and a maximum torque of 520 Nm. Its EQ Boost starter generator provides an additional short boost of 16 kW of power and 250 Nm of torque and also supplies the 48 V on-board electrical system.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'MERCEDES E63S AMG', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'mercedes-e63s-amg', '', '', '2022-08-21 22:06:31', '2022-08-21 19:06:31', '', 0, 'http://wordpress-carbook-training.ru/?post_type=car&#038;p=503', 0, 'car', '', 0),
