(518, 1, '2022-08-21 22:31:29', '2022-08-21 19:31:29', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The Ferrari Portofino M represents the evolution of the Ferrari Portofino (the letter \"M\" in the name means \"Modificata\", which indicates the changes made to the design). Spider 2+ \"Prancing Stallion\" is complemented by many new technical solutions and design elements, among which stand out the 8-speed dual-clutch transmission and the 5-position rotary switch Manettino, a completely new technology in the convertible cars of the Gran Turismo category of the factory in Maranello. Every journey aboard the Ferrari Portofino M leads towards (new) discoveries.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'FERRARI PORTOFINO', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'ferrari-portofino', '', '', '2022-08-21 22:31:30', '2022-08-21 19:31:30', '', 0, 'http://wordpress-carbook-training.ru/?post_type=car&#038;p=518', 0, 'car', '', 0),
