(521, 1, '2022-08-21 22:35:33', '2022-08-21 19:35:33', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you decide to rent an innovative Ford Mustang, get ready for a real drive. Inside the car there is everything for a comfortable trip: sports seats, a spacious interior and a roomy 140-liter trunk. An unprecedented electric car is distinguished by:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Advanced AWD all-wheel drive system that provides incredible acceleration and better handling;<br>The revolutionary SYNC 4A communication and entertainment system with machine learning and a 15.5-inch screen with an interface like a regular smartphone;<br>modern Bang &amp; Olufsen audio system with ten speakers that guarantee powerful surround sound in the Ford Mustang cabin;<br>a special panoramic glass roof with UV protection, so the car is cool in summer and warm in winter.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Renting such a car will turn an ordinary trip into an exciting journey filled with indescribable impressions and the spirit of excitement. Make yourself comfortable to fully experience the character of an advanced electric crossover.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'FORD MUSTANG MACH-E', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'ford-mustang-mach-e', '', '', '2022-08-21 22:35:34', '2022-08-21 19:35:34', '', 0, 'http://wordpress-carbook-training.ru/?post_type=car&#038;p=521', 0, 'car', '', 0);
