(527, 1, '2022-08-21 22:46:16', '2022-08-21 19:46:16', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The car, released for the anniversary, almost completely repeats the classic model. Except for minor changes.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Interior. Several nameplates with the name of the anniversary car and embossing on the headrest appeared in the cabin. The model is equipped with executive class seats with electric drive, heating and cooling upholstered in perforated semi-aniline leather;<br>Engine. The 3.0-liter TDV6 diesel offers a good balance of fuel economy and performance, as well as a fairly smooth ride.<br>Exterior. The lines have become more streamlined, moldings, grille and nameplates have acquired a golden color.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The jubilee Range Rover is first of all a luxury car, and only then an SUV. It has a chic interior, an impressive level of equipment, and there is completely no road noise inside the cabin. Renting this car will make you feel really special.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'RANGE ROVER IV', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'range-rover-iv-autobiography', '', '', '2022-08-21 22:47:25', '2022-08-21 19:47:25', '', 0, 'http://wordpress-carbook-training.ru/?post_type=car&#038;p=527', 0, 'car', '', 0),
