(535, 1, '2022-08-21 23:00:19', '2022-08-21 20:00:19', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Ferrari is a luxury that does not recognize compromises! Driving a Ferrari is the happiness of owning one of the most ”thoroughbred” cars in the world, sensations that are simply impossible to describe using standard language capabilities. Perfect ergonomics, impeccable style, shapes and structural elements, the level of electronic equipment and comfort, unbridled power and amazing sensitivity – this is an insignificant part of the advantages of Ferrari – a car of all times and peoples.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Is it worth saying that sitting behind the wheel of this perfect car has the right to count on the appropriate attitude from others? It\'s over, no! This is clear by definition - the one who managed to “climb” into this stylish “racing and tourist” salon sets the rules and priorities himself. What is, for example, a Ferrari 360 Modena Spider with a whole herd of 400 horse heads under the hood? Having accelerated to a hundred in just 4.6 seconds, revealing new possibilities of the car with every next mile, you will very soon stop comparing Ferrari with any of those cars that you had to drive before. Because there is simply nothing to compare it with.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Ferrari California', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'ferrari-california', '', '', '2022-12-04 15:17:59', '2022-12-04 12:17:59', '', 0, 'http://wordpress-carbook-training.ru/?post_type=car&#038;p=535', 0, 'car', '', 0),
