(574, 1, '2022-10-02 22:27:58', '2022-10-02 19:27:58', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Experts of the service for checking and selecting cars with mileage \"Autocode\" analyzed the statistics and named the five most popular brands of Chinese cars on the Russian market in the first half of 2022.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Haval brand takes the first place in terms of the number of checks through the \"Autocode\", Geely is in the second position, Chery is in the third. Next come Changan and FAW.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The Haval Jolidon crossover, the production of which is established at the enterprise in the Tula region, has been in a leading position for several months in a row, and its popularity continues to grow. Experts attribute this to the lack of competition in the \"price / quality\" format and difficulties with the supply of auto parts.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Chery Tiggo also remains one of the most popular models on the used car market. Cars of this brand were checked through the Autocode service more than 3,000 times in August.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>– In the first half of the year, Chinese brands managed to occupy a fairly impressive part of the market and break out into leaders among both new and used models. This trend is unlikely to change before the end of the year, analysts predict.</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Earlier JSC \"Electronic Passport\" reported that the share of Chinese cars in the Russian car market broke another record, reaching 25.9% in August. Only the domestic LADA was sold better than them.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Autocode named the most popular Chinese cars in Russia', 'Эксперты сервиса по проверке и подбору автомобилей с пробегом «Автокод» проанализировали статистику и назвали пять самых популярных марок китайских авто на российском рынке в первом полугодии 2022 года.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '308-revision-v1', '', '', '2022-10-02 22:27:58', '2022-10-02 19:27:58', '', 308, 'http://wordpress-carbook-training.ru/?p=574', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(576, 1, '2022-10-02 22:31:26', '2022-10-02 19:31:26', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>BMW 3 Series is a very popular car. Despite the global trend for crossovers, it was the \"three-piece\" that became the best-selling model of the Bavarian brand in the world by the end of 2020. But the BMW 3 Series GT is a rarer beast. The car is seriously different in size, design and driving characteristics from the usual sedan 3 series.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>BMW GT 3 series Grand Turismo (F34) was introduced in 2013. As planned, this liftback combines the spaciousness and practicality of a station wagon with the beauty and elegance of a coupe. The car is built on the basis of an elongated 3-series sedan for the Chinese market and does not share body panels with it, although it is stylistically similar in general.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Despite the interesting concept and unusual design, such a \"three-piece\" has not become popular. Sales of this model in the world and in Russia were small and the successor of the BMW Grand Turismo 3 series was not received.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 id=\"mcetoc_1gb2tbf7q3k\">What is unique about the BMW 3 Grand Turismo</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>On a test drive this time, a truly unique car. In addition to the unusual and rarity of the model itself, this particular BMW 3 series Gran Turismo is the latest car sold new in Russia.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The purchase history, as often happens, is spontaneous. Prior to that, the owner drove a BMW 1 series, which he switched to from Lada Kalina. The owner liked the cars of the Bavarian brand, and in connection with the replenishment in the family, he wanted a more spacious car. And here in Moscow were seen the last two new 3 GT, brought to Russia.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>It turned out to be almost a miracle to buy a car, because there were a lot of people who wanted to buy it. The owner even looked at the dealer database – his car is really the last one sold in Russia. After that, there were no more deliveries, the model was discontinued.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The owner is generally satisfied with the car. There were no technical problems during the year of ownership. The only thing, I had to change one of the fog lamps. Apparently, a rock hit her on the highway. The \"fog\" itself flew into the depths of the front bumper, and the owner at first thought that it had simply been stolen. As a result, everything was replaced by insurance.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Also, the owner told me that there were often cases of theft of sports M-handlebars. And as for reliability, in general, reviews of the BMW 3 series GT are positive. At the same time, our 320d Xdrive modification is considered almost the most successful of all.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Is this a real BMW? BMW 3 Series Gran Turismo Test Drive', 'BMW 3 серии – автомобиль очень популярный. Несмотря на общемировой тренд на кроссоверы, именно «трешка» по итогам 2020 года стала самой продаваемой моделью баварского бренда в мире. А вот BMW 3 серии GT – более редкий зверь. Машина серьезно отличается по габаритам, дизайну и ездовым характеристикам от обычного седана 3 серии.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '305-revision-v1', '', '', '2022-10-02 22:31:26', '2022-10-02 19:31:26', '', 305, 'http://wordpress-carbook-training.ru/?p=576', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(578, 1, '2022-10-02 22:34:50', '2022-10-02 19:34:50', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Subaru Forester has always kept apart from other crossover classmates - it has never lured the audience with fashionable design, modern interior and offered customers exclusively proven technical solutions. Coupled with a decent cross—country ability for the crossover, the Forester managed to win the love of fans, most of whom regularly use the \"Forester\" for their intended purpose - they go out of town for active recreation, hunting and fishing. The test drive of the updated Forester convinced us that, although Forik has become a little more modern, it has never lost its character.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>What\'s new?</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>There are few changes in appearance here, and an inexperienced eye will be able to see them only with a direct comparison of two cars: pre-reform and updated. The most obvious difference is the new fully LED optics: intricately shaped headlights, bracket—shaped lights and front fog lamps. Moreover, the latter are now presented in two versions: the Sport version has a design with a ring of six LED elements, and the Premium configuration has a simpler, reflex one. Only then you pay attention to the updated radiator grille with a 3D effect, new bumpers in front and rear, as well as the original design of the wheels. The dimensions of the crossover have grown by 15 mm, almost invisible to the eye, due to new bumper linings.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"left\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left\">There are no changes in the interior at all. Perhaps this is for the best, because there are fewer and fewer cars with arrow devices and physical buttons every year. A pair of color displays stands out on the center console. The upper 3.5-inch is responsible for the on-board computer, and also displays the readings of the climate system and the image from the right camera when reversing, and the lower, 8-inch, contains multimedia functions. The latter, touch, does not differ in speed or beautiful design, which is traditional for Japanese cars. But, when connecting a smartphone via Apple CarPlay or Android Auto protocols, it becomes more fun. It\'s just a pity that wireless charging Forester never appeared.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>But the \"Forika\" still has a very spacious interior and trunk, pleasant finishing materials, excellent visibility and well-designed front seats. Noise isolation, however, is worse than that of many competitors, but this moment is smoothed by the harman/ kardon audio system with decent sound.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Another feature of the new Forester is the ability of the climate system to respond to hand gestures. It is unlikely that anyone will use it, but now it is enough to clench your fist or show your palm, the temperature will rise or fall by a couple of degrees, respectively.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'We drive the updated Subaru Forester', 'Subaru Forester всегда держался особняком от других кроссоверов-одноклассников — он никогда не завлекал аудиторию модным дизайном, современным салоном и предлагал покупателям исключительно проверенные технические решения. Вкупе с приличной для кроссовера проходимостью Forester сумел завоевать любовь фанатов,', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '295-revision-v1', '', '', '2022-10-02 22:34:50', '2022-10-02 19:34:50', '', 295, 'http://wordpress-carbook-training.ru/?p=578', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(579, 1, '2022-10-02 22:43:15', '2022-10-02 19:43:15', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>First, in 2009, the Ferrari 458 Italia appeared, then, six years later, it was turned into the 488 GTB model. And now… the long-awaited new car? Alas, no. The company decided to change the traditions and continued the modernization of the former supercar. Moreover, in fact, the Ferrari F8 Tributo coupe is a \"disguised\" special version of the 488 Pista, which debuted a year ago.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The V8 3.9 turbo engine migrated to Tributo without any changes at all and develops the same 720 hp and 770 Nm. That is, the specific recoil is 185 forces per liter of working volume. The seven-stage preselective \"robot\" also remained the same. In other words, the basic version of the mid-engined Ferrari now has the same powertrain as the top modification of the last generation.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Also, the new coupe inherited a set of electronic add-ons from the Pista version. This is the SSC (Side Slip Control) control assistant in version 6.1 instead of 6.0 for the Pista model, as well as the FDE (Ferrari Dynamic Enhancer) system with the Plus prefix, which individually regulates the pressure in the braking mechanisms based on instantaneous movement parameters and allows you to more accurately dose the deceleration before the attack of turns.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The key feature of the Tributo model is a new design and improved aerodynamic efficiency by 10%. The front air intake of the S-Duct is larger than the previous one, and the new LED headlights are more compact than the previous ones, which made it possible to place additional air ducts above them to cool the brakes, which also became larger.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The transparent cover of the engine compartment now has \"gills\" for more efficient heat removal. The feed has been completely redesigned: mid-engined Ferraris have returned to the scheme with four round lights instead of two, the shape of the spoiler has been changed. All interior elements are new, but the basic layout of the front panel is the same. And the main innovation is the seven—inch touchscreen of the media system in front of the passenger.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Carbon fiber and other ultralight materials are not used as widely in the Tributo model as in the Pista coupe. Therefore, the dry weight of the novelty is greater: 1330 kg instead of 1280 kg. Although if compared with the outgoing base coupe Ferrari 488 GPIB, the new car has become lighter by 40 kg. Therefore, the dynamic parameters are also \"in the middle of the range\". The Ferrari F8 Tributo can accelerate to 100 km/h in 2.9 seconds versus 3.0 seconds for the former coupe and 2.85 seconds for the Pista version. Acceleration to 200 km/h takes 7.8 seconds, while the Ferrari 488 GTB does it in 8.3 seconds, and the Pista in 7.6 seconds. The maximum speed is more than 340 km/h.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The first public display of the Ferrari F8 Tribute coupe will take place at the Geneva Motor Show, and sales will traditionally begin in the second half of the year. And a completely new mid-engined supercar is still not far off: the car with the code F173 should be shown in May, and it will have a hybrid drive and be positioned half a step above the Tributo model.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Ferrari F8 Tributo Supercar: Italy\'s evolution continues', 'First, in 2009, the Ferrari 458 Italia appeared, then, six years later, it was turned into the 488 GTB model. And now… the long-awaited new car? Alas, no. The company decided to change the traditions and continued the modernization of the former supercar. Moreover, in fact, the Ferrari F8 Tributo coupe is a \"disguised\" special version of the 488 Pista, which debuted a year ago.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'ferrari-f8-tributo-supercar-italys-evolution-continues', '', '', '2022-10-02 22:47:01', '2022-10-02 19:47:01', '', 0, 'http://wordpress-carbook-training.ru/?p=579', 0, 'post', '', 0),
